{"tid":1553471,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「藍絲」係一種劣質基因，有就有，冇就冇。","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:47:12.000Z","uid":281401,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a655ab7a230a1f8569d15d831972a40f9bdd15c2","tid":1553471,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:25:07.000Z","msg":"突然覺得「藍絲」係一種劣質基因，有就有，冇就冇。<br />\n<br />\n家母嗰邊既親戚，姨媽到舅父，雖然全部都低學歷，但全部都清楚發生緊咩事，亦明辨是非，黃到入心。<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔識解釋，佢地真係兄弟姐妹政見取向一樣。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲呢種基因好多時候會影響人既智商，好多藍絲都係輕度智障，平時唔覺，一發作就好覺，連講句都唔清唔楚，精神有問題咁。"},{"pid":"cc1f986c4e88ecadd4c3aeca33e1649c44b908ea","tid":1553471,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"可以簡稱為奴性基因"},{"pid":"84f1c6f991d43f20bc48fdda868448d7dd24a403","tid":1553471,"uid":81353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"人性 道德 家教 <br />\nsorry 藍絲一樣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e824d931a87d7733901fb7dd2a32c57a64f4824b","tid":1553471,"uid":54921,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:34:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>愛國主義和民族主義的雙重毒害</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"50d19e99e2e3c8607e61a06a6e95cda1508b51b8","tid":1553471,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"基因唔係咁解，不過我同意藍絲好撚劣"},{"pid":"3652fc7210d9757f07aff92fce5b454fa8dcb692","tid":1553471,"uid":146535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"平時唔覺，一講就好覺<br />\n<br />\n係一出聲就好激動，原來講事實係會得罪佢"},{"pid":"1eb61ee95e7a8c2e0efc4b4c4a1c5a2a611e051f","tid":1553471,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50d19e99e2e3c8607e61a06a6e95cda1508b51b8","tid":1553471,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"基因唔係咁解，不過我同意藍絲好撚劣"},"citedBy":